text: Novobaskakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starogumerovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Kushnarenkovo, 7 km from Starogumerovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Novobaskakovo
